==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superintendence
<hw>Su`per*in*tend"ence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>superintendance</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of superintending; care
and oversight for the purpose of direction; supervision.</def>
<rj><au>Barrow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Inspection; oversight; care; direction; control;
guidance.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superintendency</ent>⟦br⟧
